libp5glove
------------------------------------------
The Essential Reality P5 Data Glove is a USB device that reports 5 finger
positions, and 8 X/Y/Z IR locations.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.0-0.212.g6af8fea4bbad
  libGL1-19.1.6-1
  libGLU1-9.0.2-1
  libglut3-3.4.0-1
  libp5glove-devel-0.10-1bl2
  libp5glove0-0.10-1bl2
  libusb0-1.2.6.0-2
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20240607-1
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libGL-devel-19.1.6-1
  libGLU-devel-9.0.2-1
  libglut-devel-3.4.0-1
  libtool-2.5.3-1
  libusb-devel-1.2.6.0-2
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/ezrec/libp5glove

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/ezrec/libp5glove/archive/refs/tags/v0.10.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libp5glove-0.10-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libp5glove-0.10-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libp5glove-0.10-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libp5glove-0.10-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libp5glove0-0.10-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libp5glove-devel-0.10-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libp5glove)
  /usr/bin/p5dump.exe
  /usr/bin/p5hand.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libp5glove.README
  /usr/share/doc/libp5glove/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libp5glove/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libp5glove/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libp5glove/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libp5glove/README
  /usr/share/doc/libp5glove/TODO.txt

(libp5glove0)
  /usr/bin/cygp5glove-0.dll

(libp5glove-devel)
  /usr/include/p5glove.h
  /usr/lib/libp5glove.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libp5glove.pc

